### Health
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/health

### Start session
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/v1/start
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "icon_set": "aws4"
}

### Chat generate (replace session_id)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/v1/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "session_id": "<session_id>",
  "file_name": "api-example",
  "message": "User sends POST to API Gateway and stores in RDS postgres"
}

### Chat update (replace session_id)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/v1/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "session_id": "<session_id>",
  "message": "add EventBridge daily trigger and connect EventBridge -> ECS Fargate Task -> Redshift"
}

### Get file by session
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/v1/file?session_id=<session_id>

### Understand active diagram by session
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/v1/diagram/understand
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "session_id": "<session_id>"
}

### Redefine plan (no mutation)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/v1/diagram/redefine/plan
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "session_id": "<session_id>",
  "message": "add EventBridge and connect EventBridge -> ECS Service"
}

### Redefine apply (mutates XML)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/v1/diagram/redefine/apply
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "session_id": "<session_id>",
  "message": "add EventBridge and connect EventBridge -> ECS Service"
}

### Validate by file path
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/v1/validate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "file_path": "api-example.drawio"
}

### Session details
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/v1/session/<session_id>
